t([[The ground suddenly shakes under your feet and a giant worm appears to gobble you up!
You could try to escape using the Rod of Recall or accept your fate.]], [[갑자기 발밑의 땅이 흔들리고, 거대한 벌레가 튀어나와서 당신을 집어삼키려 합니다!
